Subject: [PATCH v5 04/11] drm/mediatek: gamma: Improve and simplify HW LUT calculation
Date:   Thu,  1 Jun 2023 14:10:15 +0200
Message-Id: <20230601121022.2401844-5-angelogioacchino.delregno@collabora.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.40.1
